name: TestReport.status
title: TestReport.status
purpose: Data Elements are defined for each element to assist in questionnaire construction etc

element.definition: The current state of this test report.
element.comment:
The status represents where the execution is currently within the test script execution life cycle.

This element is labeled as a modifier because the status contains codes that mark the resource as not currently valid.
element.isModifierReason: This element is labelled as a modifier because it is a status element that contains status entered-in-error which means that the resource should not be treated as valid

binding.description: The current status of the test report.
